How to build PMlib and to install.


1) Procedure of normal compilation

   Edit environmental variables in a make_setting file for a target machine, then 'make'.
   

2) Procedure of compilation from FFVC solver
   
   Edit environmental variables in a FFVC/src/FFV/make_setting.* file for a target machine.
   Execute 'make' command at FFVC/src/FFV/ directory.


Compiled module will be placed in lib/ directory.
